'''花園橋'''（'''Garden Bridge'''）是曾计划要在[[倫敦|倫敦]][[泰晤士河|泰晤士河]]上興建的一座行人橋，但该计划以失败告终。這座橋的構想在1998年就由女演員[[喬安娜·拉姆利|喬安娜·拉姆利]]提出了，<ref name="Indie-HG" /> 此後交由[[托馬斯·赫斯維克|托馬斯·赫斯維克]]設計，由[[倫敦交通局|倫敦交通局]]委任[[奧雅納|奧雅納]]集團協助。<ref name="Architizer" /> 預計橋上會栽種許多樹木形成一個花園，此橋也因此得名。<ref name="TUTH" /><ref name="OCeallaigh" /> 2013年11月1日花園橋信託（Garden Bridge Trust）成立，目的是對此橋的建築進行監督。<ref name="Indie-HG" /><ref name="BBCViews" />

花園橋的長度大約為{{convert|367|m}},<ref name="I Like Architecture" /> 最寬處寬約{{convert|30|m}}。此橋自河北岸[[聖殿站|聖殿站]]附近的阿倫德爾街（Arundel Street）延伸出來，<ref name="TUTH" /> 在[[南岸中心|南岸中心]]落地。<ref name="OCeallaigh" /> 建成之後可與[[紐約市|紐約市]]的[[高線公園|高線公園]]、[[巴黎|巴黎]]的[[綠蔭步道|綠蔭步道]]相媲美。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ft.com/intl/cms/s/0/7d418d2e-590b-11e3-a7cb-00144feabdc0.html#axzz2mJhB5bSW|title=London garden bridge poised for £30m funding from Treasury|work=Financial Times}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/the_eye/2013/12/05/the_garden_bridge_london_s_answer_to_the_high_line.html|title=The Garden Bridge: London's answer to the High Line?|work=Slate Magazine|accessdate=2014-12-18|archive-date=2014-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209072047/http://www.slate.com/blogs/the_eye/2013/12/05/the_garden_bridge_london_s_answer_to_the_high_line.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2014/sep/14/london-garden-bridge-barking-up-wrong-tree|title=London’s Garden bridge: barking up the wrong tree?|author=Rowan Moore|work=the Guardian|accessdate=2014-12-18|archive-date=2015-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221044540/http://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2014/sep/14/london-garden-bridge-barking-up-wrong-tree|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.architectsjournal.co.uk/footprint/the-garden-bridge-is-not-londons-answer-to-the-new-york-high-line/8673289.article|title=The Garden Bridge is not London's answer to the New York High Line|work=architectsjournal.co.uk|accessdate=2014-12-18|archive-date=2015-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150412031008/http://www.architectsjournal.co.uk/footprint/the-garden-bridge-is-not-londons-answer-to-the-new-york-high-line/8673289.article|dead-url=no}}</ref>

{{As of|2014年7月}}，花園橋的預算已達到1.75億英鎊，這年5月完整的方案已經提交出來了，[[蘭貝斯|蘭貝斯]]市政廳在11月批准了此方案，預計此橋將在2018年之前完工。<ref name="Guardian-July2014" /><ref name="Planning-2014" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-30015011|title=BBC News - London's River Thames garden bridge backed by council|work=BBC News|accessdate=2014-12-18|archive-date=2014-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220130512/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-30015011|dead-url=no}}</ref> 但后来此计划因花销和维护成本太高，伦敦市长宣布不会为其买单，花园桥信托公司在2017年8月14日宣布放弃该计划<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gardenbridge.london/news/article/garden-bridge-trust-announces-the-closure-of-the-project|title=Garden Bridge Trust announces the closure of the project|website=Garden Bridge - Introducing London’s iconic new landmark|accessdate=14 August 2017|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814104622/https://www.gardenbridge.london/news/article/garden-bridge-trust-announces-the-closure-of-the-project|archivedate=2017年8月14日|df=}}</ref>。這項失敗的計劃共花去460萬鎊公款<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-40921373|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|title=London's Garden Bridge project officially abandoned|date=14 August 2017|accessdate=2018-04-11|archive-date=2018-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180305145538/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-40921373|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

